What is GruntJS?
A task runner for automating reptitive tasks.

--

What kind of tasks?
* Minification
* Concatentation
* Pre- and post-processing files
* If you script it, they will come...

--

Who uses Grunt?
* Twitter
* jQuery
* Adobe
* Modernizr

--

Where does it work?
* In the command line, using npm and Node.js.

--

Works and is shareable between Mac, Windows, and Linux.

--

Installing Grunt

http://gruntjs.com/getting-started

npm install -g grunt-cli

--